  - font: 14px Nunito Regular
  - 상태: default, hover, visited

### Divider
- **Or Divider**: 소셜/이메일 구분
  - line: stroke #030229
  - text: "Or" 16px SemiBold #030229

### Icon Button
- **Nav Icon**: 사이드바 아이콘 24x24
  - color: #030229 (기본) | #605bff (active)
- **Logout Icon**: 17x17

### Date Picker
- **Date Input**: 시작/종료 날짜 선택
  - size: 130x40
  - background: #ffffff
  - cornerRadius: 5
  - text: 14px SemiBold #030229

### Tooltip
- **Chart Tooltip**: 차트 호버 툴팁
  - background: #ffffff
  - border/shadow: #030229
  - cornerRadius: 10
  - 화살표: 14x14

### Table
- **Data Table**: Recent Orders 등
  - header: 12px Nunito Regular #030229
  - row: 12px Regular, bg #fafafb (alternate)
  - border: #030229 (1px)

### Nav Item
- **Sidebar Nav**: 메뉴 항목
  - active: bg gradient #aca9ff, text #605bff
  - inactive: text #030229
  - font: 16px SemiBold
  - padding: 24px 아이콘 + 텍스트

